OL,3,CParents appear in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurdering baby in hospital
OL,6,FThe parents of a two-week-old baby
OL,7,Fhave appeared in court charged with
OL,8,Fmurder.
OL,10,FSophie Staddon, 20, and Daniel Gunter,
OL,11,F25 are accused of killing baby Brendon
OL,12,FStaddon at Yeovil District Hospital on
OL,13,F5 March.
OL,15,FBoth defendants, of no fixed address,
OL,16,Fhave also been charged with causing or
OL,17,Fallowing Brendon's death.
