OL,3,CParents appear in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurdering baby in hospital
OL,6,FThat charge alleges that "being a
OL,7,Fmember of the same household as and
OL,8,Fhaving had frequent contact" with
OL,9,FBrendon, they either caused his death
OL,10,For did not protect him from a
OL,11,Fforeseeable "significant risk of
OL,12,Fserious physical harm".
OL,14,FBrendon was two weeks old when he died
OL,15,Fat around 5am on Tuesday 5 March at
OL,16,Fthe hospital, where he was an
OL,17,Finpatient.
