OL,3,CParents appear in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurdering baby in hospital
OL,6,FStaddon and Gunter appeared before
OL,7,FTaunton Magistrates' Court on Friday 8
OL,8,FMarch, where they spoke to confirm
OL,9,Ftheir name, date of birth and address.
OL,11,FDuring Staddon's court appearance,
OL,12,FPresiding Justice Victoria McNiven
OL,13,Ftold Staddon: "This matter is being
OL,14,Fsent to Bristol Crown Court on 11
OL,15,FMarch at 10am. In the meantime, you
OL,16,Fare being remanded in custody."
OL,18,FDeborah Hodges appeared for the
OL,19,Fprosecution during the short hearing,
OL,20,Fwhile Tony Miles represented Staddon.
