OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police previously
OL,7,Fsaid officers were called to the
OL,8,Fhospital, where Brendon was an
OL,9,Finpatient, by staff.
OL,11,FAn investigation was launched by the
OL,12,Fforce's major crime investigation team
OL,13,Fa short time later.
OL,15,FDetective Inspector Mark Newbury, of
OL,16,FAvon and Somerset Police, said: "This
OL,17,Fis a particularly tragic case in which
OL,18,Fa very young baby has died, and our
OL,19,Fthoughts are with Brendon's loved ones
OL,20,Fduring this time.
